{{Top|leg}}
'''Energy harvesters''' were used on [[Genarius]]. They collected the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmosphere]] to extract the energy stored within. A number worked around the abandoned [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Nub Saar]].

{{Veh-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
"Energy harvester" seemed to be a generic term to refer to the ships used to mine Genarius, such as the [[AR-25 Bubbleship transport]].

